text: Robert Herrmann (December 11, 1869 - 1919) was an American gymnast. He competed in four events at the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1869 births Category:1919 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Milwaukee
